    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132890/extras/ecc7636800e46caa1c1ce5d83be4850a.poster.avif?t=1769690378\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132890/extras/ecc7636800e46caa1c1ce5d83be4850a.webm?t=1769690378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132890/extras/ecc7636800e46caa1c1ce5d83be4850a.mp4?t=1769690378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>请查看下方的<strong>“完整版游戏特性”</strong>部分，了解当前抢先体验版本的状态以及即将到来的完整版发布信息。</u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132890/extras/6c1cb001c4eaa2e109626ff4cb425f05.avif?t=1769690378\" width=1536 height=143 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新手教程与入门流程：<strong>包含探索与战斗机制*</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2个可玩角色</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的卡牌</strong>：可发现大量卡牌并构建强力组合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡牌升级系统</strong>与<strong>游戏内商店</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>角色技能</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的敌人：<strong>普通、精英和首领敌人</strong>，拥有多种攻击方式和效果</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种节点类型</strong>：每种节点都有一系列独特的互动可能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>初始指令</strong>：可自定义，让你能根据当前卡组调整玩法风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>痕迹效应</strong>：根据你的行动提升游戏难度</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>试玩版中的流程使用固定种子且仅包含1个层次。完整版将包含完全随机生成、每次都会变化的3层流程！</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132890/extras/18c51f4e2b12a062bff265dbfbb18c48.avif?t=1769690378\" width=1536 height=143 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抢先体验版状态</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2个角色，拥有完整的卡组（每个角色超过70张独特卡牌）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3层流程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4个难度等级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更多种类的节点、驱动程式、卡牌和指令</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完整版将新增内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进度系统</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>额外角色</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>事件系统</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成就系统</strong></p></li></ul>",
